            <p>R has nothing to do with "roman script". R is used for RFC_822.</p>

<p>Also according to ISO in italian and poland the month names are NOT written in roman script.
It this is really incorrect than please add a issue at CLDR (unicode.org) who maintain the CLDR database where ZF relies to.</p>

<p>But you can archive such a behaviour by using Zend_Measure, to convert the month number into roman notation.</p>

